.DT
sacrifice
$MUDNAME$ Command Help
sacrifice

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
sacrifice - Used to sacrifice items to a god.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
sacrifice <item(s)>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
By sacrificing items you draw the attention of your god and offer the items
to him (or as it may be, her), as a result you are moved closer to the
preferred alignment of your god.  The effectiveness and difficulty of this
command is based on the number and value of items sacrificed and your bonus
in faith.rituals.special
.EP

.SH Example
.SP 5 5
> sacrifice swords
.EI
.SP 5 5
You hold out two leaf blade swords and utter a prayer to draw the attention of
Dilabi, offering them as a gift for his greater glory.
Two leaf blade swords crumble and you are left with a small pile of forest
green dust.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
faith, religion
.EP
